Website - Bhuvan Govt of Andhra Pradesh NTR Vaidya Seva Trust
Website URL - https://bhuvan-app1.nrsc.gov.in/ntr
Website Content Details - 
bhuvan Govt of Andhra Pradesh NTR Vaidya Seva Trust is a geospatial portal developed by the National Remote Sensing Centre (NRSC) of the Indian Space Research Organisation (ISRO) in collaboration with the Government of Andhra Pradesh. The portal provides a comprehensive view of the health care facilities in the state, including government hospitals, private hospitals, and diagnostic centers. The portal can be used to locate the nearest health care facility, to find out about the services offered by a facility, and to book appointments online.

The portal is available in English and Telugu languages. It can be accessed on the web or through a mobile app.

The portal provides the following features:

Hospital search: Users can search for hospitals by location, type, or scheme.
Hospital profile: The hospital profile provides information about the hospital's location, contact details, services offered, and fees.
Appointment booking: Users can book appointments online for government hospitals and private hospitals that participate in the scheme.
Other features: The portal also provides information about health care schemes, health statistics, and health resources.
The NTR Vaidya Seva Trust is a valuable resource for the people of Andhra Pradesh. It provides access to information about health care facilities and services, making it easier for people to access the care they need.
